body: It looks like the _out functions (example: `binary_cross_entropy_backward_out`) are not called anywhere and not accessible from Python (from doing a grep). They're accessible as a part of the ATen API, though (so `tensor.binary_cross_entropy_backward_out` would work in ATen).
